Module org.opengis.geoapi
Package org.opengis.referencing.operation

Interface ConicProjection

All Superinterfaces:
Conversion, CoordinateOperation, IdentifiedObject, Projection, SingleOperation
public interface ConicProjection extends Projection
Base interface for conical map projections.
Since:
1.0
See Also:
  • ProjectedCRS
  • Conic projection on MathWorld
Departure from OGC/ISO abstract specification:
Addition of element not in the ISO/OGC specification This interface is not part of the ISO specification. It has been added in GeoAPI at user request, in order to provide a way to know the kind of map projection.
